[[tabview]]
[[tab Disclaimer/Licensing]]
[[=]]
+ NOTE
As always, all assets I use are //always// checked to be CC-compliant. If it isn't and you have a problem with it, feel free to contact me on Discord[[footnote]] kidnamedfinger4153 [[/footnote]], as Wikidot isn't exactly known as being //reliant// when it comes to communication.

On that note, if you have requests, questions, or commissions,[[footnote]] **WINK WINK. NUDGE NUDGE.**[[/footnote]] //also// feel free to message me.

Just be clear in your initial messages; I usually block anyone who comes off as slightly resembling spam.

With all that out of the way, hope you like my shit.
[[/=]]
